    "title": "Hiring Category Manager at Mothercare India",
    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at Mothercare India. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Category Manager to strengthen our Tiruchirappalli-based team.\n\nAbout Mothercare India:\nMothercare India is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Conduct competitor analysis and market benchmarking\n• Manage product listings, pricing, and promotions on the platform\n• Analyze sales data and customer behavior to drive revenue growth\n• Develop and implement category growth strategies\n• Coordinate with vendors and suppliers for inventory management\n• Manage marketplace relationships with Amazon, Flipkart, and Meesho\n• Collaborate with logistics partners to ensure timely delivery\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Ed / M.Ed from a recognized institution\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Performance Marketing\n• Proficiency in Facebook Ads\n• Proficiency in Retention Marketing\n• Proficiency in SEO/SEM\n• Proficiency in Content Writing\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n• Proficiency in Digital Marketing\n• Proficiency in Customer Segmentation\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Flexible working hours\n• Referral bonus program\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Tiruchirappalli, Tamil Nadu, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Mothercare India!",
